snippet.title: Traversal DEMO - 2025 Trailer
snippet.description:
While traversing through several islands in this action adventure game, you'll need to help the islanders, solve puzzles and survive to make your way back home.

Download now for free!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3334450
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/traversal/528927
Itch.io: https://chillincreative.itch.io/traversal

Check out the website!
https://chillincreative.cc/traversal
You can add Traversal to your RSS feed to follow the game!

Alternatively, follow Traversal's development on social media!
Bluesky: https://bsky.app/profile/chillincreative.cc
Tumblr: https://www.tumblr.com/traversalcc
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Just_Chillin_95
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/traversal/
